==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mouser
<hw>Mous"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A cat that
catches mice; <as>as, a good <ex>mouser</ex> is better than a dozen
mousetraps</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who pries about on the lookout for
something.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mousetail</ent>⟦br⟧
